{"tid":2178540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷遊行盼紐維爾舊生簽美斯","createTime":"2020-08-28T12:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:40:14.000Z","uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad0a684eb6c0856109b1364f0d58d967fccdf19","tid":2178540,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】自美斯要求離開巴塞隆拿後，不少球會都他有轉會傳聞，最新一間球會便是阿甲的紐維爾舊生體育會。<br />\n據西班牙《馬卡報》報道，阿甲紐維爾舊生體育會希望可以將美斯（Lionel Messi）帶回當地聯賽。美斯6歲便加盟了家鄉球會紐維爾舊生體育會的青年軍，至2000年才轉投巴塞隆拿，據指美斯一直都是紐維爾舊生的忠實球迷。 有見美斯要求離開巴塞，紐維爾舊生的球迷亦要求球會簽下這名「青訓產品」，更打算在羅薩里奧，美斯出生的城市遊行，希望可以看到美斯回到家鄉球會效力。不過因為新型冠狀病毒正大流行，今次遊行的球迷將會駕駛車輛於城市中慢駛，預計會有過百名球迷參加。 雖然紐維爾舊生有心，但其財政亦無法負擔今次轉會，加上現時曼城、巴黎聖日耳門及國際米蘭都有意簽下這名巨星，紐維爾舊生成功的機會亦不算高<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%9B%BC%E7%B4%90%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%B0%BD%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-110716285.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%259B%25BC%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2588%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25AF-110716285.html&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b48a3623\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%9B%BC%E7%B4%90%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%B0%BD%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-110716285.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/brfootball/status/1299286497858904065?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrfootball%2Fstatus%2F1299286497858904065%3Fs%3D21&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=bcfce079\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrfootball%2Fstatus%2F1299286497858904065%3Fs%3D21&h=b45430bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/brfootball/status/1299286497858904065?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/deportes_